name: Skinner's RUSH
description:
Happy birthday Candii!
For full immersion, please say "teehee you can't catch me! You can't catch meee~" in Alexandria's voice when you play.
Alexandria and Skinner are AiCandii's horror couple!

Features
- Run away from Skinner but slowly enough for him to stay invested in the chase!
- Try to beat your high score!
- Not much more features, I made this in like 4 hours.
